Class Review

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Review
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Review
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class contains all information of one piece of review - including the reviewing date, rating, reviewing content, reviewing Movie and reviewer's name.
    Version:
    1.0
